'''''Saranthe''''' is a genus of plants native to Brazil and Paraguay, described as a genus in 1861.<ref name="Joannatomassacci">[http://apps.kew.org/wcsp/namedetail.do?name_id=262669 Kew World Checklist of Selected Plant Families, ''Saranthe'']</ref><ref>[https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/29244150#page/149/mode/1up August Wilhelm Eichler. 1884.  Abhandlungen der Königlichen Akademie der Wissenschaften zu Berlin 1883: 85.] description in Latin, commentary in German</ref><ref>[http://www.tropicos.org/Name/40029548 Tropicos ''Saranthe'' Eichler ]</ref>

; Species<ref name="Joannatomassacci"/>
{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|
* ''[[Saranthe composita]]'' - [[Espírito Santo]], [[Rio de Janeiro (state)|Rio de Janeiro]]
* ''[[Saranthe eichleri]]'' - [[Paraguay]], [[Paraná (state)|Paraná]], [[São Paulo (state)|São Paulo]]<ref>[http://www.tropicos.org/Name/19700187?tab=specimens Tropicos, specimen list for ''Saranthe eichleri'' ]</ref>
* ''[[Saranthe gladioli]]'' - [[Rio de Janeiro (state)|Rio de Janeiro]]
* ''[[Saranthe glumacea]]'' - [[Rio de Janeiro (state)|Rio de Janeiro]]
* ''[[Saranthe klotzschiana]]'' - [[Rio de Janeiro (state)|Rio de Janeiro]], [[Bahia]]
* ''[[Saranthe leptostachya]]'' - [[Rio de Janeiro (state)|Rio de Janeiro]], [[Espírito Santo]]
* ''[[Saranthe madagascariensis]]'' - [[Rio de Janeiro (state)|Rio de Janeiro]], [[Bahia]]
* ''[[Saranthe membranacea]]'' - [[Minas Gerais]]
* ''[[Saranthe tenuifolia]]'' - [[Rio de Janeiro (state)|Rio de Janeiro]]
* ''[[Saranthe ustulata]]'' - [[Santa Catarina (state)|Santa Catarina]] }}

